---
title: Figgy Jam Stuffed Chicken with Walnut Dusted Green Beans
description: Sweet sticky figgy goodness all wrapped up in a juicy and tender chicken breast. It's the classy weeknight dinner you've been waiting for, all that's missing is a bow!
